@startuml 16-state-customs-declaration
title State Machine — Customs Declaration Lifecycle

[*] --> Pending : declaration submitted

Pending --> InReview : assigned to officer\nor auto-flagged (risk)

InReview --> Cleared : officer approves\nor auto-clearance
InReview --> Held : missing documents\nor inspection required
InReview --> Rejected : compliance failure

Held --> InReview : documents received
Held --> Rejected : deadline exceeded

Cleared --> [*]
Rejected --> [*]

note right of Pending
  Kafka: customs.declarations
  Agent: customs-agent
  MCP: customs-mcp
end note

note bottom of InReview
  Risk score thresholds:
  < 0.3  → auto-clear eligible
  0.3-0.7 → manual review
  > 0.7  → hold + inspect
end note

@enduml
